Class ResettableHttpServletResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.strohalm.cyclos.http.ResettableHttpServletResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, javax.servlet.ServletResponse, Resettable

    public class ResettableHttpServletResponse
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse, Resettable
    An HttpServletResponse which wraps another response, keeping track of changes. Any changes can be applied or reset.
    Author:
    luis
